The '''Lifetrees''' were the trees of the '''Life-orchards''' that drained the [[Sharu/Legends|Sharu's]] intelligence temporarily. When [[Lando Calrissian/Legends|Lando Calrissian]] activated the [[Mindharp of Sharu/Legends|Mindharp]] of [[Sharu/Legends|Sharu]], he deactivated the intelligence-draining.

